snippet.title: TypeOut Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out this new game from us here at NovelKeys! TypeOut! This isn't your typical typing test. Unlock power-ups, create a load-out, and battle your way through prompts as fast and accurately as you can to allocate power-ups and strategically attack your opponents in an effort to slow them down.

Will you get typed out in TypeOut? Available for early access now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1802270/TypeOut/
